        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": ">However an upper-case pattern still doesn't work properly with 'smartcase' and \"longest\": I<C-N> only completes InputEvent while I<C-P> only completes INPUT_MAP.\n\n@zeertzjq That is the same behaviour that was in nvim 0.12.\n\nHowever, I agree that it'd be great to fix but not sure how it'd work unless it detected smartcase and changed the user input to lowercase (which seems bad).",
